{"tid":2252574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"方力申深明運動員退役難處 初入行性格內向曾被誤會囂張","createTime":"2020-10-21T14:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T15:37:00.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"164c5d54f01e15cbe5429913fab3b881e893928d","tid":2252574,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"方力申今日以退役運動員學長身份到銅鑼灣出席「香港運動員就業及教育計劃嘉許典禮」，計劃主要是協剛退役的運動員轉型及心理輔導。小方當年準備入大學前，也曾獲陳念慈擔任學姊身份幫助過，他覺得運動員退役後再轉換新環境，往往會因為以往訓練時對自我要求高，變得一時難以適應，他說：「我初入行時做訪問成日答案短過問題，又唔識主動講料，就畀人錯覺覺得我寸，其實我係內向。」"},{"pid":"fbcc2c74985fa4e7672d85a66114d9ff6369e630","tid":2252574,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"經過6、7年時間，直至《美女廚房》後，小方明白到要放鬆心情去傾，愈來愈進步，問到可有想過放棄？他說：「放棄就冇，只係心入面諗，一係快啲醒目，一係被觀眾淘汰，試過有段時間有人群恐懼症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oH1ySnF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoH1ySnF.gif&h=2238f683&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49a1ce5d28709366d517189654bfccb979251535","tid":2252574,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"至於小方的游泳學校在疫情下大受影響，差不多停課3個月，現在有限度復課，幸好有股東一齊分擔開支，及政府補助，期望政府有進一步協助。"},{"pid":"ccdf2f2dc8f089033a1d708a6cfb33689c05e750","tid":2252574,"uid":43061,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"跟住你串我阿嘛"},{"pid":"88a72835c2c79ab98507720d7abb67ce1338ec00","tid":2252574,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LIbpmoTAn5bmplokdYaBUgeKSUo=/535x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HCIGDKETHNBNRMGGKO754XVQFI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLIbpmoTAn5bmplokdYaBUgeKSUo%3D%2F535x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHCIGDKETHNBNRMGGKO754XVQFI.JPG&h=00a16d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自言曾遇過退役轉型的困難，初入行更被指囂張。"},{"pid":"2d091a99489b5ef5cec26dee4e7755efbcf779da","tid":2252574,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YKmh66yORf-h4fj-KBo2hpwIBAo=/535x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CXDAQZZVPNFG5F2MQXWSO5YLOI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYKmh66yORf-h4fj-KBo2hpwIBAo%3D%2F535x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCXDAQZZVPNFG5F2MQXWSO5YLOI.JPG&h=fdc88c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n游泳學校在疫情下大受影響，差不多停課3個月。"},{"pid":"f76791c1190d1560086f902e75322eae2fe70438","tid":2252574,"uid":54623,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"一路幫開香港既澳洲手足Drew Pavlou眾籌緊,請大家幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/drew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fdrew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8eb1fee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/drew-pavlou-uq-fighting-fund</a>"},{"pid":"479597602e7558250a55714973c914c4740883bf","tid":2252574,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"不死小申 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a77a930aca0e2d81659b5622e67c1951ff140c","tid":2252574,"uid":7323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"跟住你串我吖嘛"},{"pid":"9181fa0f95061640bc4b8fccbe539526fbbdb941","tid":2252574,"uid":55493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"初入行畀人誤會串<br />\n<br />\n做耐咗就真係串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so